data.Name: Still Woozy
data.Bio: Sven Eric Gamsky, known professionally as Still Woozy (born June 23, 1992), is an American singer and songwriter from Oakland, California. He is signed to to Interscope Records. Gamsky grew up in Moraga, California, in the San Francisco Bay Area. After he went viral with the R&B-inflected "Goodie Bag" in 2017, he continued to release one-off tracks until presenting the Lately EP in 2019. It included another streaming hit, "Habit."
